## What's Changed
* fix mutable error by @anarchyologist in https://github.com/exakty/VeraAPI/pull/341
* Update deploy-action-stage2.yml by @versecafe in https://github.com/exakty/VeraAPI/pull/340
* add user field for dreports by @anarchyologist in https://github.com/exakty/VeraAPI/pull/342

## New Contributors
* @versecafe made their first contribution in https://github.com/exakty/VeraAPI/pull/340

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/exakty/VeraAPI/compare/v1.3.38...v1.3.39
